      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=z90rcpct4c]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=z90rcpct4c]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nlthf74sqz]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nlthf74sqz]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=onvsygwqy3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=onvsygwqy3]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=a51xudar7u]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=a51xudar7u]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jw6alwisjm]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jw6alwisjm]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n8jg7uh8sk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n8jg7uh8sk]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=yv85tmlsvl]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=yv85tmlsvl]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=wt3q3lnrsd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=wt3q3lnrsd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jril1zjir9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jril1zjir9]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=v3dzfnandf]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=v3dzfnandf]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=zp84vbturq]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zp84vbturq]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pp61zshgnh]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pp61zshgnh]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=rqlwygmzba]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=rqlwygmzba]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=l58520ro74]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=l58520ro74]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=s0db97kcvo]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=s0db97kcvo]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709808120&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=426\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599883858/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709808120&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1075\" data-width=\"1915\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612171999\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599883858\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"46\" data-media-id=\"b98f595c-3060-4cb9-a69b-31417abf5db0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709808120&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=852 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709808120&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=426 1x\" /></span><p>In rendering, you&rsquo;ll use texture maps of all kinds, constantly.</p><p>This set of lessons will guide you through how RenderMan handles textures, how to add randomization to those textures, and if you&rsquo;re painting your textures in Mari or Substance Painter, you&rsquo;ll learn how to correctly export and import those into RenderMan so you get visual parity when rendering. </p><h1 id=\"Textures-StartHere\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"n8jg7uh8sk\">Start Here</span></strong></h1><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608796673/Texture+Basics\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608796673\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"TexturesThumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612401265\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"TexturesThumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599883858\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"46\" data-media-id=\"6d82399e-5f72-4cf6-ad36-b18bbeef952d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jw6alwisjm\">Texture Basics</span></strong><br />Learn the basics of how RenderMan handles textures.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/392822785/Controlling+Textures\" data-linked-resource-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"TexturesThumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612401265\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"TexturesThumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599883858\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"46\" data-media-id=\"6d82399e-5f72-4cf6-ad36-b18bbeef952d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/TexturesThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758709754357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jril1zjir9\">Controlling Textures</span></strong><br />Manifolds control textures &hellip; Learn to control Manifolds!</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/625672304/Black+White\" data-linked-reso