embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Painter_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Painter_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760000468011&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599883858/Painter_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760000468011&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"622690344\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Painter_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599883858\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"46\" data-media-id=\"42655c81-6cea-4051-bef1-7f5b949709e4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Painter_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760000468011&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599883858/Painter_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760000468011&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"s0db97kcvo\">Substance Painter</span></strong><br />Learn how to get your materials from Substance Painter into RenderMan.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657162522/RazorBack+Displacement\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657162522\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"razor.jpg\" wid